<subSubSection id="C368652E935D8E00F2AAF8BAFB2AF841" pageId="4" pageNumber="488" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BCD36A5935D8E00F2AAF8BAFB2AF841" blockId="4.[151,1437,1832,2039]" pageId="4" pageNumber="488">
The specimen here designated as 
<typeStatus id="54C98807935D8E00F036F8BAFDA3F889" box="[523,626,1832,1858]" pageId="4" pageNumber="488">lectotype</typeStatus>
is a male bearing the labels: “ 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D26935D8E00F182F8BAFBD6F889" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1829" box="[959,1031,1832,1858]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="488" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="dispar">
<emphasis id="B906EAB7935D8E00F182F8BAFBD6F889" box="[959,1031,1832,1858]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="488">dispar</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
mihi in Gallia mer.” and “ 
<typeStatus id="54C98807935D8E00F714F8BAFA4DF889" box="[1321,1436,1832,1858]" pageId="4" pageNumber="488">Lectotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D26935D8E00F28AF8DEFDDEF8AD" authority="Dejean, 1829" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1829" box="[183,527,1868,1894]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="488" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="dispar">
<emphasis id="B906EAB7935D8E00F28AF8DEFEA0F8AD" box="[183,369,1868,1894]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="488">Harpalus dispar</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B54935D8E00F344F8DEFDDEF8AD" author="Dejean, P. F. M. A." box="[377,527,1868,1894]" pageId="4" pageNumber="488" refId="ref10732" refString="Dejean, P. F. M. A. (1829) Species general des coleopteres de la collection de M. le Comte Dejean. Tome quatrieme. Mequignon- Marvis, Paris, vii + 520 pp." type="book" year="1829">Dejean, 1829</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
desig. by J. Serrano”. There is also a 
<typeStatus id="54C98807935D8E00F1FCF8DEFB89F8AD" box="[961,1112,1868,1894]" pageId="4" pageNumber="488">paralectotype</typeStatus>
with labels: “male symbol”, “Gallia mer./ Perpignan”, “ 
<typeStatus id="54C98807935D8E00F3F9F8E2FDB3F841" box="[452,610,1904,1930]" pageId="4" pageNumber="488">Paralectotype</typeStatus>
” and “ 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D26935D8E00F092F8E2FBD2F841" authority="Dejean, 1829" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1829" box="[687,1027,1904,1930]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="488" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="dispar">
<emphasis id="B906EAB7935D8E00F092F8E2FCB9F841" box="[687,872,1904,1930]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="488">Harpalus dispar</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B54935D8E00F153F8E2FBD2F841" author="Dejean, P. F. M. A." box="[878,1027,1904,1930]" pageId="4" pageNumber="488" refId="ref10732" refString="Dejean, P. F. M. A. (1829) Species general des coleopteres de la collection de M. le Comte Dejean. Tome quatrieme. Mequignon- Marvis, Paris, vii + 520 pp." type="book" year="1829">Dejean, 1829</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
desig. by J. Serrano”.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C368652E935D8E00F2FAF806FBF3F83C" pageId="4" pageNumber="488" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BCD36A5935D8E00F2FAF806FBF3F83C" blockId="4.[151,1437,1832,2039]" pageId="4" pageNumber="488">
The 
<typeStatus id="54C98807935D8E00F2C7F806FEB0F865" box="[250,353,1940,1966]" pageId="4" pageNumber="488">lectotype</typeStatus>
hereby designated shows the morphology currently considered to represent the nominal subspecies (e.g., 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B54935D8E00F336F82BFE0BF819" author="Fuente de la, J. M." box="[267,474,1976,2003]" pageId="4" pageNumber="488" refId="ref10490" refString="Fuente de la, J. M. (1927) Tablas analiticas para la clasificacion de los coleopteros de la Peninsula Iberica. Adephaga: I Cicindelidae, II Carabidae. J. Bosch, Barcelona, 415 pp." type="book" year="1927">Fuente, 1927: 226</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B54935D8E00F3DAF82AFD6EF818" author="Jeannel, R." box="[487,703,1976,2003]" pageId="4" pageNumber="488" pagination="572 - 1173" refId="ref11231" refString="Jeannel, R. (1942) Coleopteres carabiques. Deuxieme partie. Faune de France 40. Librairie de la Faculte des Sciences, Paris, pp. 572 - 1173." type="book chapter" year="1942">Jeannel, 1942: 657</bibRefCitation>
). These two authors considered the validity of the genus 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D26935D8E00F779F82AFE80F83D" authority="Des Gozis, 1882" authorityName="Des Gozis" authorityYear="1882" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Artabas" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="488" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B906EAB7935D8E00F779F82AFA4CF819" box="[1348,1437,1976,2002]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="488">Artabas</emphasis>
Des Gozis, 1882
</taxonomicName>
and included within it 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D26935D8E00F069F84EFCDCF83D" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1829" box="[596,781,2012,2038]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="488" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="dispar">
<emphasis id="B906EAB7935D8E00F069F84EFCDCF83D" box="[596,781,2012,2038]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="488">Harpalus dispar</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D26935D8E00F17EF84FFBCAF83D" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1829" box="[835,1051,2013,2038]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="488" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="punctatostriatus">
<emphasis id="B906EAB7935D8E00F17EF84FFBCAF83D" box="[835,1051,2013,2038]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="488">H. punctatostriatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C368652E935C8E01F2FAFF05FCDDFF31" pageId="5" pageNumber="489" type="reference_group">
<paragraph id="8BCD36A5935C8E01F2FAFF05FCDDFF31" blockId="5.[151,1436,150,250]" pageId="5" pageNumber="489">
<taxonomicName id="4C724D26935C8E01F2FAFF05FEAEFF7A" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1829" box="[199,383,151,177]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="489" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="dispar">
<emphasis id="B906EAB7935C8E01F2FAFF05FEAEFF7A" box="[199,383,151,177]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="489">Harpalus dispar</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
includes three subspecies (
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B54935C8E01F091FF05FC79FF7A" author="Kataev, B. M. &amp; Wrase, D. W." box="[684,936,150,177]" pageId="5" pageNumber="489" pagination="319 - 330" refId="ref11494" refString="Kataev, B. M. &amp; Wrase, D. W. (1995) Three new and two little-known Palearctic species of the genus Harpalus Latr. (Coleoptera, Carabidae). Linzer Biologische Beitrage, 27, 319 - 330." type="journal article" year="1995">Kataev &amp; Wrase 1995</bibRefCitation>
): 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D26935C8E01F187FF05FADAFF7A" authority="Dejean, 1829" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1829" box="[954,1291,151,177]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="489" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="dispar" subSpecies="dispar">
<emphasis id="B906EAB7935C8E01F187FF05FBA0FF7A" box="[954,1137,151,177]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="489">H. dispar dispar</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B54935C8E01F64AFF05FADAFF7A" author="Dejean, P. F. M. A." box="[1143,1291,151,177]" pageId="5" pageNumber="489" refId="ref10732" refString="Dejean, P. F. M. A. (1829) Species general des coleopteres de la collection de M. le Comte Dejean. Tome quatrieme. Mequignon- Marvis, Paris, vii + 520 pp." type="book" year="1829">Dejean, 1829</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
(West Mediterranean), 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D26935C8E01F325FF29FD46FF1E" authority="Gebler, 1830" authorityName="Gebler" authorityYear="1830" box="[280,663,187,213]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="489" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="dispar" subSpecies="splendens">
<emphasis id="B906EAB7935C8E01F325FF29FE2AFF1E" box="[280,507,187,213]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="489">H. dispar splendens</emphasis>
Gebler, 1830
</taxonomicName>
(from 
<collectingRegion id="49B6F847935C8E01F0D5FF29FCE6FF1E" box="[744,823,187,213]" country="Turkmenistan" name="Balkan Welayaty" pageId="5" pageNumber="489">Balkan</collectingRegion>
Peninsula to West Siberia) and 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D26935C8E01F69AFF29FE9CFF32" authority="Menetries, 1832" authorityName="Menetries" authorityYear="1832" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="489" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="dispar" subSpecies="elegantulus">
<emphasis id="B906EAB7935C8E01F69AFF29FA4DFF1E" box="[1191,1436,187,213]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="489">H. dispar elegantulus</emphasis>
Menetries, 1832
</taxonomicName>
(from Transcaucasus to 
<collectingCountry id="F3657635935C8E01F05DFF4DFCD1FF31" box="[608,768,223,250]" name="Turkmenistan" pageId="5" pageNumber="489">Turkmenistan</collectingCountry>
).
</paragraph>
